{"TopicId":155005,"ForumId":16,"TopicTitle":"\u0026quot;Switch To\u0026quot; Problem","CreatedByName":"oguz","CreatedById":145037,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-14T20:24:33Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"oguz","CreatedById":145037,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-14T20:24:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI don\u0027t know what happened, but right now when i click on something, i automatically switch to that object that i clicked on with mouse. How can i disable it? I cannot even detach objects anymore \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-01-14T20:24:54Z\u0022 title=\u002201/14/2017 08:24  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EJanuary 14, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by oguz\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Benjamin Kerman","CreatedById":172792,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-14T20:28:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGo into your controls in the main menu. You can change all the listings: probably something is screwed up in there.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"bewing","CreatedById":154251,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-14T20:28:32Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt sounds like it happened suddenly? It might be a mouse problem? So it\u0027s getting a doubleclick instead of a singleclick. Try putting a new battery in the mouse, maybe?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Benjamin Kerman","CreatedById":172792,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-14T20:29:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222921845\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022155005\u